CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 30, 1950, pg. 13, reads: "Visitors - Visiting at the home of Mr. and Mrs. George Gaines during the holidays were Mr. and Mrs. Howard Morgan of Baltimore, shown here with the Gaineses' son.  Mr. Morgan is the brother of popular Mrs. Eleanor Davis. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Howard Morgan, Mrs. Morgan, and young George "Toby" Gaines in apartment above Gaines Funeral Home, Auburn Street, East Liberty
